OL,5, A bus driver has been sacked after     
OL,6, driving through a red light and nearly 
OL,7, hitting a seven-year-old girl.         
OL,9,FNewport Transport said it was "deeply  
OL,10,Fsorry for the distress" to Courtney and
OL,11,Fher family after the bus narrowly      
OL,12,Favoided her on Somerton Road.          
OL,14,FCCTV footage showed she began to cross 
OL,15,Fwhen the green man appeared, but had to
OL,16,Fquickly turn around to avoid the bus.  
OL,18,FThe company said it would "always take 
OL,19,Fswift action" if staff did not drive   
OL,20,Fprofessionally.                        
